text: Godou ihoo hagadau aaloho huogodoo gu de langahia e ginaadou goodou, digaula gu hagalee haa manawa i goodou. Au gu hai baahi adu gi goodou gadoo be di hagadaumee, godou hagaduadua koia gu kono adu gi goodou, idimaa go godou huaidu la koia gu logowaahee, mo godou haihai huaidu koia gu llauehaa huoloo.
